# Ragnarok plugin servers — copy to plugins.env (next to run.command) and edit.
#
# One line per plugin server:  <absolute server dir>|<run command>
# Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
# run.command launches each server whose directory exists, on Ragnarok startup.
#
# The server can live anywhere on disk (e.g. another repo). If the server dir
# has a .venv, run.command activates it automatically (the plugin's deps win);
# otherwise it falls back to Ragnarok's Python. An explicit interpreter in the
# command (e.g. .venv/bin/python …) always takes precedence.
#
# Example (Dashboard Importer, plugins_V3 — the backend-session generation):
# /Users/you/simplePyPSA_KR/plugins_V3/ragnarok-dashboard-importer/backend|python server.py --port 8765
